    • Method Detail

      • genCode

        protected CompiledMethod genCode()
        By definition, abstract methods do not have associated code. Therefore, this method will return an error handling method from RuntimeEntrypoints that will raise an AbstractMethodError when it is invoked.
        Specified by:
        genCode in class RVMMethod
        Returns:
        an object representing the compiled method
        See Also:
